620714682_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Kjx1lDdOZIgQ7kNvgEDDjnx&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD-BqU3cjR5cclK8TmsSO8FNBbKIrOX1mox_vn36Dzh8A&oe=66DD88BF"}, "display_name": "Detour Bus Demo", "keywords": [], "long_description": "ARRIVING SUMMER 2022\nTHIS DEMO INCLUDES THE FIRST LEVEL OF DETOUR BUS\n\nDetour Bus is a VR construction-comedy adventure, where you build ridiculous winding highways, to take the dysfunctional Flowers family on a road trip across Post-Infrastructure America. Nostalgia junkie Daddy Flowers aims to revive his family's bonds before the end of summer vacation, but stuck together in a restored microbus, workaholic Momma, communist-in-training Junior, and social-media-baby Goldie have a lot more to fight about than unite over. Meanwhile, the open road is under threat; you'll have to get in the construction groove to take on corrupt Senator Joseph McCarthief\u2019s attempts to turn all freeways into pay-to-drive tunnels and reclaim your right to transportation.\n\nAccessibility Considerations:\none-button controls\ncaptioning\ndyslexia friendly fonts\nartificial locomotion incl. snap turning, smooth moving\nheight calibration\none-controller mode\nno-reach 3DoF mode\nbuttons-only mode\nfull button remapping", "short_description": "Snap together inconvenient road pieces to build ridiculously convoluted highways, and guide the dysfunctional Flowers family on a psychedelic road trip across post-infrastructure America."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://latestageinteractive.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Late Stage Interactive", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://detourbus.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["CASUAL", "PUZZLE", "TRAVEL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "N